# ITAGAKI-SYSTEM: COMPOSITIONAL RESOLUTION ENGINE (TRUE COMPOSITIONAL SHANNON LIMIT)
# Core Equation: Delta_min = sqrt( (Z_alpha^2 * (pi_i + pi_j)) / (wt + Z_alpha^2) )
# Focus: Direct independent contrast between Physical Resolution Floor and Signal Delta
# Developed by: Tatsuki Itagaki (Eliminated Circular Variance Bias)
